headline: The drug discovery research for lecanemab awarded the 9th Bioindustry Award by the Japan Bioindustry Association
summary: BioArctic AB's (publ) (Nasdaq Stockholm: BIOA B) partner Eisai announced today that the drug discovery research for lecanemab (product name Leqembi®), an antibody indicated for early Alzheimer's disease which was co-developed by Eisai and BioArctic, has received the 9th Bioindustry Award from the Japan Bioindustry Association (JBA).
